channel.title: My internets broken
channel.description: This is making me mad. I have three computers in my family, we share the internet connection. The internet works fine on the other two computers, but on mine it works for like 30 minutes/not at all. When I go to My computer->Network connections->Show?-> and press fix, it says "Could not empty NetBT". Somebody help me, I asked on IRC but no one has a clue... could this be because I scanned 4 million IP's with a trojan scanner and my ISP banned me?
